<h1>Ev's Burgers!</h1>

<h2>burgers Up for Eatin!!(current menu)</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
    {{#unless edible}}
      {{> burgers/single-burger edible=true}}
    {{/unless}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Burgers to come back to(apparently not the instant-add section)</h2>

<ul>
  {{#each burgers}}
    {{#if edible}}
      {{> burgers/single-burger edible=false}}
    {{/if}}
  {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>Add a Burger</h2>
<form class="create-form">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="ca">Burger of the Day:</label>
    <input type="text" id="ca" name="name">
  </div>
